5:
"Watch Out! Random Attacks
Continue in the Streets!"
For real? Headlines these days, I
swear...
9:
Haven't you heard, Alk? There's been
a ton of reports about it!
14:
Why am I getting a sense of déjà vu
here...
18: Could you tell us what you've heard?
21:
Apparently, someone's been going
after men who are walking alone...
Yanking off their hair, throwing some
mystery concoction over 'em, then
running off.
26:
Wait, that's it? The post made it
sound like we had a serial killer or
something. They're just stealing hair?
29:
A crime's still a crime, right? Let me
know if you find out anything! There
could be a reward in it for you this
time!
33:
Why do you look like you just sucked
on a lemon, Nimbus?
36:
Sorry... Just got this wicked chill
down my spine. Think I'm gonna
head home and sleep...
40:
Not often that Nimbus doesn't feel
well. Do you think he caught a cold?
43:
Perhaps he has indigestion. Should
we grab him some medicine?
50:
M-mercy, please! I don't have that
much hair left! Let me and my
balding head go!
56:
Oh, boy... So Sohvi is the culprit. As
soon as I heard Lilie tell the story, I
figured it might be her, but...
59:
H-help me! This chick's trying to
pluck every last hair from my body!
62:
The evidence is damning. But Sohvi,
why would you do this?
65:
Ain't it obvious? I'm trying to make
me a fur-growing potion! Y'see,
brewing it is proving to be a lot
tougher than I first thought.
68:
Ugh, I'm way behind schedule! I
should be fluffy and furry and living
it up as Nimbus's wifey already! All
these setbacks are REALLY PISSING
ME OFF!
74: L-let's just take a deep breath, okay?
79:
Anyway! I've got work to do with all
these hair samples! Don't get in my
way, got it?!
83:
I'm sorry, but I'm afraid we can't just
let you do what you please.
88:
I get where you're coming from—
Actually, let's not kid ourselves. I
don't.
91:
But if you call it quits now, you still
have time to make amends for your
crimes!
95:
My WHAT? So you ARE going to get
between me and my dear Nimbus!
100:
Whoa, whoa, whoa! Light, any ideas?
Preferably something that'll save our
hides from getting diced up!
103:
Tch... Do we have no choice but to
fight?
108:
We... We're victims of the
Hair-Stealing Slasher!
111:
If you're victims... Then are you here
to take revenge against your
assailant?
113:
Well, can't say the thought didn't
cross our minds at first! But things
are different now! This crazy chick
changed our lives!
116:
You know how she poured some
weird potion on us, right? This
morning, we woke up with a whole
new head of lustrous, smooth hair!
118:
She even restored my hairline! I
don't know how I can ever repay her!
121:
I... I see. That's impressive... I suppose
that means you won't press charges?
126:
Did you hear that, Sohvi? Your stuff
worked, AND nobody's mad at you!
Isn't that nice?
130: HOW COULD ANY OF THIS BE NICE?!
141:
Hair is SUPPOSED to grow out of your
SCALP!
143:
Making concoctions for that is EASY!
But growing FUR on your BODY ISN'T!
MY EXPERIMENT FAILED!
144:
HOW AM I EVER SUPPOSED TO GET MY
NIMBY-WIMBY TO NOTICE ME IF I'M
NOT GROWING A FULL COAT?!
148:
But these IDIOTS are CELEBRATING
my FAILURE! Oh, I'll do more than
TAKE HAIRS THIS TIME!
153: RUN ALL YOU WANT. I'LL FIND YOU!
158:
Hoooold your horses! You've made
your point! Sorry for not taking your
worries seriously!
160:
I know the perfect way to apologize!
A gift you'll really love! Let those folks
go, and I'll tell you how to get it!
167:
Err... I know a way to get Nimbus's fur
without causing a fuss or breaking
any rules!
172:
I'm sure it'll serve you way better
than any run-of-the-mill hair you'll
find out here! So... How about it?
177: Alk. You're a true bro after all!
181:
Sohvi, you're cleaning? Allow me to
assist.
186:
Oh! Stella? It's fine, totally fiiine! I've
got this! Doing it because I want to!
189:
Is that right? Thank you for your
service.
194:
Yes... Shed more, you hairy hunk...
Hair number 284...
Mm... smells sultry...
